_sText: Dust2045 by Tatu Eugen - www.tatueugen.info After 45 years dust is going to be destroyed. The old terrorists is back to destroy dust for ever, the cts team are sent in last mission for save dust and old city, the terrorists team discovers an new site for plant bomb, on this time cts team must stop all bombs planted in site a and b. Save the dust.
